      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "thanks. one more thing, if the weave is super tight like we want for the high-end stuff, does that actually impact the durability or how much air can pass through? i'm trying to figure out if a denser weave might make the material too stiff or less breathable.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
